title: Trump: No Justice for Katie Johnson? (Jeffrey Epstein)
description:
Contrary to the claim that nobody has ever seen the accuser face-to-face, that nobody verified her identity (or existence), and contrary to the claim that Emily Shugerman was the only journalist to ever interview her, you will find that Katie Johnson was interviewed by journalists reporting for the Daily Mail: https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3894806/Woman-alleged-raped-Donald-Trump-13-Jeffrey-Epstein-sex-party-DROPS-case-casting-doubt-truth-claims.html
Further links to articles related to (and quoted in the video) ensue. https://www.newsreview.com/reno/content/epstein-trump-and-news-review/28779363/
https://www.revelist.com/politics/i-talked-with-katie-johnson/3573/but-when-i-talked-to-steve-baer-a-conservative-donor-who-has-been-rallying-media-attention-around-this-case-and-against-trump-he-told-me-a-different-version-of-the-story/14
https://sacramento.newsreview.com/2019/10/21/wait-katie-johnson-actually-exists/
http://thememoryhole2.org/blog/doe-v-trump
The final link contains the legal documents (from the abandoned court case) as PDFs.
